    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It's been totally pampered since day one, always garage-kept, and it drives like an absolute dream. You won't find a single scratch or hiccup anywhere! If you're looking for that brand-new feeling without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come see it!",
