    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that remains in true showroom condition. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, entirely free of rock chips, swirls, or imperfections, having been preserved under a professional ceramic coating and strictly garage-kept. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather bolsters show zero wear, the carpets are spotless, and every interior surface feels factory-fresh. Mechanically, it is absolute perfection, backed by a comprehensive, folder-thick service history and recent preventative maintenance. Every button, switch, and electronic sensor functions exactly as intended. Never driven in inclement weather and maintained with an obsessive attention to detail, this car represents the pinnacle of its class for a discerning collector who demands nothing less than a pristine example.",
      "price": 48500.0,
