      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, you\u2019ve gotta see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied this car since day one and it\u2019s basically spent its whole life tucked away in a garage. It looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s virtually brand new and ready for a new home, this is definitely the one. Drop me a message and let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
