      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving, naturally aspirated precision. Under the hood, the S54 inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a seamless 8,000 RPM redline, maintained with rigorous attention to the Vanos system and valve clearances. The chassis is structurally immaculate, featuring preventive rear subframe reinforcement and a factory-spec limited-slip differential that ensures surgical power delivery through the Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. With zero mechanical lash and a pristine exterior that retains its original factory luster, this specimen offers the tactile steering feedback and balanced weight distribution that defined an era of performance engineering.",
